headline: Does Coca Cola Still Offer Value After Its Recent 54.4% Five Year Share Price Run?
summary: Wondering if Coca Cola at around $70 a share is still a sweet deal or if most of the upside has already been poured out? You are not alone, and that is exactly what we are going to unpack here. Despite a recent 3.3% pullback over the last week, the stock is still up 2.6% over 30 days, 13.9% year to date, and 54.4% over 5 years.
